{"tid":1647970,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣「卡提諾狂新聞」力挺香港示威者","createTime":"2019-10-12T03:45:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T04:06:41.000Z","uid":205394,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"60dc4a0bfba378d436f61ccbcbbafc8aca543ed7","tid":1647970,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:45:53.000Z","msg":"卡提諾狂新聞係台灣網上媒體<br />\n每星期都會將國際唔同搞笑既新聞造一個一至五名既排名榜<br />\n用幽默搞笑既方式去講呢D新聞<br />\n<br />\n反送中活動以黎狂新聞都一直幫香港示威者做宣傳<br />\n上星期第一位就係香港蒙面法,重播左一段好熱血既示威者吶喊<br />\n今個星期第一名同第二名都排左香港反送中示威<br />\n<br />\n台灣文宣戰來講,狂新聞出一條片,勝過我地出幾萬張文宣<br />\n強烈建議大家訂閱同支持狂新聞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TQAHZLz9gyI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTQAHZLz9gyI&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uIoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=bab806e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TQAHZLz9gyI</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mv0HVkFZpO8&amp;t=1s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMv0HVkFZpO8%26t%3D1s&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uIoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=9f2b64c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mv0HVkFZpO8&amp;t=1s</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Fight for Freedom <br />\nStand with Hong Kong</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"2ad0bede9b96049b9208b40dfdd344a50f5772cf","tid":1647970,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:46:41.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"4bc6dbe5e53529ace27a1ac55c981148a31a0be2","tid":1647970,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:46:57.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"7cabdd6d4dc5feca10d90aa19fdb17c1502cf94e","tid":1647970,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T03:47:08.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"cf3331baaa99c02d01850473e0fb85c15830f070","tid":16479